'''拉維·特賈'''（Ravi Teja，泰盧固語：రవి తేజ），本名'''拉維·香卡·拉裘·布帕提拉裘'''（Ravi Shankar Raju Bhupatiraju），出生於1968年1月26日，[[安得拉邦|安得拉邦]]之[[西哥達瓦里縣|西哥達瓦里區]]<ref>[http://www.filmibeat.com/celebs/ravi-teja/biography.html Ravi Teja's Biography] {{Wayback|url=http://www.filmibeat.com/celebs/ravi-teja/biography.html |date=20190829114943 }}. One India. 2012/8/29.</ref>。九十年代起以綠葉角色起家，得過南迪獎之特別評審獎與最佳男演員獎，為印度泰盧固語影業（Tollywood）當紅演員之一<ref>[http://www.telugupeople.com/news/article_00079218_Ravi_Teja_back_in_form.asp Ravi Teja back in form] {{Wayback|url=http://www.telugupeople.com/news/article_00079218_Ravi_Teja_back_in_form.asp |date=20160325000819 }}. Telugu People. 2012/12/21.</ref> <ref name="synonymous">[http://www.indiaglitz.com/i-dont-like-serious-films-ravi-teja-telugu-news-63143 I don't like serious films] {{Wayback|url=http://www.indiaglitz.com/i-dont-like-serious-films-ravi-teja-telugu-news-63143 |date=20201025170146 }}. IndiaGlitz. 2011/1/17.</ref>。

==簡介==
拉維·特賈之父親Rajgopal Raju Bhupatiraju為藥師，母親Rajya Lakshmi為家庭主婦，有兩名弟弟Raghu Raju與Bharath Raju<ref>[http://www.raagalahari.com/stars/interviews/113/ravi-teja.aspx Ravi Teja Interview] {{Wayback|url=http://www.raagalahari.com/stars/interviews/113/ravi-teja.aspx |date=20150924084020 }}. Ragalahari. 2005/7/18.</ref>。2002年，他娶了表親Kalyani，已育有一名女兒Mokshadh與一名兒子Mahadhan。求學時代因父親工作的關係，時常在北印度一帶遷徙不定<ref>[http://www.telugucolours.com/id1-pid16-chR/profile/ravi-teja Ravi Teja's Profile] {{Wayback|url=http://www.telugucolours.com/id1-pid16-chR/profile/ravi-teja |date=20130524083358 }}. Telugu Colours.</ref>。能操流利之[[泰盧固語|泰盧固語]]、[[印地語|印地語]]、[[馬拉提語|馬拉地語]]、[[坦米爾語|泰米爾語]]、[[康納達語|卡納達語]]，為人低調、不喜曝光<ref>[http://www.cinegoer.net/telugu-cinema/interviews/interview-with-ravi-teja.html Exclusive Interview With Ravi Teja] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cinegoer.net/telugu-cinema/interviews/interview-with-ravi-teja.html |date=20160730192106 }}. CineGoer. 2009/5/8.</ref> <ref>[http://www.deccanchronicle.com/140927/entertainment-tollywood/article/i-keep-family-and-films-apart-always-ravi-teja I keep family and films apart always] {{Wayback|url=http://www.deccanchronicle.com/140927/entertainment-tollywood/article/i-keep-family-and-films-apart-always-ravi-teja |date=20201024092811 }}. Deccan Chronicle. 2014/9/27.</ref> <ref>[http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/telugu/movies/news/Im-actually-a-little-shy-Ravi-Teja/articleshow/43814047.cms I'm actually a little shy] {{Wayback|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/telugu/movies/news/Im-actually-a-little-shy-Ravi-Teja/articleshow/43814047.cms |date=20150604054721 }}. The Times of India. 2014/9/29.</ref>。

==職業生涯==
1988年，拉維·特賈於[[維傑亞瓦達|維傑亞瓦達]]的Siddhartha College取得藝術學士學位後，即前往[[清奈|清奈]]，以助理導演之職務涉足電影業，也兼跑龍套擔任綠葉角色以糊口<ref>[http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/regional/news-interviews/YVS-Gunasekhar-Ravi-were-rommates/articleshow/8626083.cms?referral=PM YVS, Gunasekhar & Ravi were rommates] {{Wayback|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/regional/news-interviews/YVS-Gunasekhar-Ravi-were-rommates/articleshow/8626083.cms?referral=PM |date=20160305022510 }}. The Times of India. 2011/5/29.</ref>。首次在1997年的[[w:en:Sindooram|《Sindhooram》]]中獲得擔任主角的機會，此片榮獲印度國家電影獎之最佳泰盧固語劇情片獎。1999年的[[w:en:Nee_Kosam|《Nee Kosam》]]與2002年的[[w:en:Khadgam|《Khadgam》]]則為他贏得了南迪獎之特別評審獎<ref name="Awards">[http://www.cineradham.com/telugucinema/nandiawards.html The Nandi Awards] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140130004927/http://cineradham.com/telugucinema/nandiawards.html |date=2014-01-30 }}. CineRadham.</ref>。

2002年之[[w:en:Idiot_(2002_film)|《Idiot》]]為拉維·特賈職業生涯首部超級賣座片<ref>[http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/telugu/movies/news/Ravi-Teja-exclusive-interview/articleshow/20797431.cms 'Idiot' catapulted the actor into superstardom] {{Wayback|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/telugu/movies/news/Ravi-Teja-exclusive-interview/articleshow/20797431.cms |date=20150514203411 }}. The Times of India. 2013/6/27.</ref>，之後連續數部作品皆獲成功，使其在泰盧固語影業嚴重的家族壟斷之下異軍突起<ref>[http://www.gulte.com/movienews/9037/Big-Fight-in-Tollywood-draws-Attention Big Fight in Tollywood draws Attention] {{Wayback|url=http://www.gulte.com/movienews/9037/Big-Fight-in-Tollywood-draws-Attention |date=20150924041001 }}. Gulte. 2012/7/26.</ref>，為繼[[赤拉尼維|赤拉尼維]]之後，唯一一個沒有影業世家背景<ref name="synonymous"/>，而成為當紅演員的男星<ref>[http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/telugu/movies/news/Tollywoods-family-economics-decoded/articleshow/21802398.cms Tollywood's family economics decoded] {{Wayback|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/telugu/movies/news/Tollywoods-family-economics-decoded/articleshow/21802398.cms |date=20210126125211 }}. The Times of India. 2013/8/13.</ref>。2008年的[[w:en:Neninthe|《Neninthe》]]叫好不叫座，但卻為他贏得了南迪獎之最佳男演員獎<ref name="Awards"/>。

{{Quote box|width=30%|align=left|quote=" 我喜歡人們進戲院盡情歡享我的電影，人生苦短，我不想在我的作品中呈現那些瑣碎與無奈，娛樂大眾是我的要務，觀眾們愛看我搞笑與開掛，即使是女性觀眾也討厭我扮演軟弱的哭包角色，所以我不拍嚴肅片與情感片。"|source= 拉維·特賈（節錄）<ref name="synonymous"/> <ref name="So"/>}}
拉維·特賈因其作品偏向大眾喜好、出演之電影極少讓片商賠錢、表演風格瘋狂、會演戲同時也是[[阿米塔布·巴沙坎|阿米塔·巴強]]的影迷，而擁有"群眾大君"（Mass Maharaja）、"托萊塢最可靠之男星"（The Most Reliable Hero in Tollywood）、"怪咖之星"（Crazy Star）、"安得拉阿米塔"（Andhra Amitabh）等封號<ref>[http://totalwoods.in/2011/05/exclusive-interview-with-ravi-teja-by-totalwoods/ Exclusive Interview With Ravi Teja] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141020153054/http://totalwoods.in/2011/05/exclusive-interview-with-ravi-teja-by-totalwoods/ |date=2014-10-20 }}. Totalwoods. 2011/5/1.</ref> <ref>[http://www.manatelugumovies.net/power-problems-raviteja/ Power problems for Ravi Teja] {{Wayback|url=http://www.manatelugumovies.net/power-problems-raviteja/ |date=20160304120149 }}. Mana Telugu Movies. 2014/8/31.</ref> <ref>[http://www.greatandhra.com/movies/movie-news/andhra-amitabhs-dual-role-in-hindi-film--48737.html Andhra Amitabh's dual role in Hindi film] {{Wayback|url=http://www.greatandhra.com/movies/movie-news/andhra-amitabhs-dual-role-in-hindi-film--48737.html |date=20160305032914 }}. Great Andhra. 2013/8/10.</ref>。

出道二十多年來，他曾嘗試過各種戲路，其中以無賴形象之喜劇角色最獲盛名與讚譽，表演特色在於對白之表達語調、異常豐富之肢體語言、有活力、瘋癲<ref>[http://english.tupaki.com/enews/view/Dil-Raju-Comments-on-Ravi-Teja/70496 Dil Raju Comments on Ravi Teja] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141016070333/http://english.tupaki.com/enews/view/Dil-Raju-Comments-on-Ravi-Teja/70496 |date=2014-10-16 }}. Tupaki. 2014/8/11.</ref> <ref>[http://www.thehansindia.com/posts/index/2014-09-11/Mass-Maharaja-Ravi-Teja-107342 Mass Maharaja Ravi Teja] {{Wayback|url=http://www.thehansindia.com/posts/index/2014-09-11/Mass-Maharaja-Ravi-Teja-107342 |date=20160304191549 }}. The Hans India. 2014/9/11.</ref>。作品幾乎都帶有喜劇色彩<ref name="So">[http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/telugu/movies/news/Ravi-Teja-gives-Akshay-Kumar-a-run-for-his-money/articleshow/14771389.cms Ravi Teja gives Akshay Kumar a run for his money] {{Wayback|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/telugu/movies/news/Ravi-Teja-gives-Akshay-Kumar-a-run-for-his-money/articleshow/14771389.cms |date=20201030192431 }}. The Times of India. 2012/7/9.</ref>，知名代表作有《Idiot》、《拳之路》、《Venky》、《熱血無賴》、《杜拜先生》、《刺激》、《王者歸來》、《愛情臥底》、《維拉》、《幸運的無賴》、《狂傲》、《麻辣警長》等。

